==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Brooklime
<hw>Brook"lime`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A plant (<spn>Veronica Beccabunga</spn>), with flowers, usually
blue, in axillary racemes. The American species is <spn>Veronica
Americana</spn>.</def> <altsp>[Formerly written <asp>broklempe</asp> or
<asp>broklympe</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Brook mint</ent>⟦br⟧
